      "description": "$4,900 - Honest, inexpensive transportation for someone who wants a running, driving car at a low entry price. This is a rough driver with noticeable cosmetic wear and an overall tired presentation, but it can still serve as a basic commuter or project for the right buyer. It\u2019s not close to show condition and should be bought with the expectation that it will need ongoing attention, but it offers affordable usability for a realistic buyer.",
