    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Reliable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a budget-minded buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking practical, low-cost driving or a project opportunity, but it remains a solid chance to get behind the wheel without a major investment. A sensible option for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone needing inexpensive everyday transportation.",
